<br>
On another note:<br>
<br>
I don't like us being censored on the spell issue, and moved from the General area that 99.99% of all people read first. <br>
<br>
Fal asked that:<br>
<br>
Also, note. PoP spells are NOT final yet. Leave them be until Verant has confirmed what they are. Thanks.<br>
<br>
I respectfully disagre with Fal. People can't wait and remain silent, because by silence you are giving tenative approval.<br>
<br>
If we can get a POP only section as I proposed on a seperate thread there would be no confusion where to look for this info, but moving them all over the board just makes them not be read. As it is not no one will know the best places to look for information.<br>
<br>
Even more importantly, if Verant reads this board they will look in the most obvious place for feedback, and that is the General section or a dedicated PoP location, and not read every forum to find our thoughts, so what we discuss may never be seen by Verant because they will now know where the information was scattered too.<br>
<br>
With 6 or less weeks to go, we can't afford not to discuss what we are seeing and thinking on these issues. We need a central location for all of PoP discussion. If not in general. Than a PoP section only. But keep all those threads in one easy to locate place.<br>
